## Variables

+ Site = project field location
+ PlantID = plant unique identifier              
+ Planting Date  =  date of planting      
+ First Bagging Date  =  first time bagging date
+ Last Bagging Date   =  last date of bagging
+ Total Bags = cummulate number of bagged flowers per plant
+ Number OfBagging Days = total days of bagging the plant
+ Accession Name = accession name
